<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Coburg</head><p>Der Rat gewährt Hans Karl, Bürger zu Coburg, Geleit bis Johannistag wegen seiner Klage vor dem Stadtgericht zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_62" id="29v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_62_r4l19">Der Stat cʒu <expan>Kob<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_62_r4l20"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l21">hanſen karls ewrs mitburgers wegen / laſſen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erſ<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l22"><expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ vns derſelb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / Als wir des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l23"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit ein abſchrıft <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> in di hirynne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan></del> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l24">in diſem brıef / Vnd alſo iſt eʒ / daʒ derſelb ewr mitburger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l25">von <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſere<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> recht </del> hıe vor des Reichs Rihter oder vor vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l26">recht <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> wil 
<add><ab facs="#facs_62_r1l1">des vvir Jm gern </ab><ab facs="#facs_62_r1l2"><expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> vmb <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſein </del> ſache dıe Er mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l27">cʒuhandeln hat / <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> Er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hıecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſant <expan>Joh<ex>ans</ex></expan> tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l28">cʒu <expan>Sünvvende<ex>n</ex></expan> ſchierſt her cʒu vns gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kümt / So ſol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l30">Er 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu vns vnd von vns bey </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_62_r4l29">cʒu vns bey vns vnd von 
<del rend="strikethrough">vns </del></ab></add> vns ein ſleht ſicher geleẏte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r4l31"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ongeuerde </ab>
<add cert="unknown">
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l3">be </ab></add> </div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_62" id="29v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu <expan>Kob<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Hansen Karls, ewrs mitburgers, wegen,
                        lassen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz uns derselb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, als wir des
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit ein abschrift
                                <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> in disem brief. Und also ist ez, daz
                        derselb ewr mitburger von <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unsere<ex>n</ex></expan> hie vor des reichs rihter oder vor uns recht
                                <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> wil, <add>des wir im gern
                                    <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan></add> umb
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache, die er mit
                            <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czuhandeln hat, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app>
<note><q type="date">sant <expan>joh<ex>ans</ex></expan> tag czu
                                            <expan>sünwende<ex>n</ex></expan> schierst</q>
                                24.06.1408</note>
</app> her czu uns gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kümt, so sol er
                            <add>czu uns, bey uns und von </add> uns ein sleht sicher geleyte
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für uns und die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ongeverde.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
